OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister on Friday described
OL,8,Fthe killing of veteran politician Ann
OL,9,FWiddecombe as "shocking", and said it
OL,10,Fwas important for everyone to rise
OL,11,Fabove political differences
OL,13,FA 26-year-old white British man has
OL,14,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,15,Fmurdering former MP and MEP Ann
OL,16,FWiddecombe.
OL,18,FThe ex-Tory prisons minister was found
OL,19,Fdead at her home in Haytor on Dartmoor
OL,20,Fon Thursday after sustaining serious
OL,21,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
