CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FWiddecombe, who was 78, later became a
OL,8,FBrexit Party MEP and subsequently a
OL,9,FReform UK spokeswoman.
OL,11,FShe also found fame outside politics
OL,12,Fafter starring in Strictly Come
OL,13,FDancing and Celebrity Big Brother.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
