PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police Assistant
OL,8,FChief Constable Matt Longman said the
OL,9,F26-year-old suspect was arrested at an
OL,10,Faddress in Newton Abbot on Friday.
OL,12,FHe said the case was "not being
OL,13,Ftreated as terrorism" and there was
OL,14,F"no information" at this time to
OL,15,Fsuggest it was a "politically
OL,16,Fmotivated crime".
OL,26,@tD@VOUuD@UO]vD@AOUvD@PO]wD@ROUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
