PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FHe said: "This is an extremely tragic
OL,8,Fincident. Our thoughts are very much
OL,9,Fwith the family and friends of Miss
OL,10,FWiddecombe in this very difficult
OL,11,Ftime."
OL,13,FPolice are remaining "open-minded"
OL,14,Fabout the motive for the attack and it
OL,15,Fwas too early to comment on whether
OL,16,Fthe suspect was known to Miss
OL,17,FWiddecombe.
OL,19,FWatch the Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,20,Fpress conference here
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@FO]uD@VOUuD@bO]
