PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer urged
OL,8,Fpeople to come together across
OL,9,Fpolitical divides following the murder.
OL,11,FSpeaking to reporters in his Chequers
OL,12,Fcountry retreat, he said he had spoken
OL,13,Fto his likely successor Andy Burnham,
OL,14,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch and Reform
OL,15,FUK's Nigel Farage to "urge everybody
OL,16,Fto come together at a moment like
OL,17,Fthis".
OL,26,@wD@VOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
