PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FHe said: "This is really shocking
OL,8,Fnews, and my thoughts, I think all of
OL,9,Four thoughts, will be with the family
OL,10,Fand friends of Ann Widdecombe at this
OL,11,Fawful time for them.
OL,13,F"Ann was a distinguished politician
OL,14,Fover many, many years with many
OL,15,Fachievements, and it's a huge, huge
OL,16,Floss."
OL,18,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,19,Fit was important to "rise above any
OL,20,Fpolitical differences".
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOUxD@FO]{D@UOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
