PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,F"Ann gave a lifetime of public
OL,8,Fservice, and it's absolutely right
OL,9,Fthat the police put all their
OL,10,Fresources into investigating this as
OL,11,Fswiftly as possible."
OL,13,FWiddecombe's management firm Cloud 9
OL,14,Furged people with information to
OL,15,Fcontact the police and said: "We are
OL,16,Fabsolutely devastated by this news
OL,17,Ffollowing a very traumatic and
OL,18,Fupsetting 24 hours."
OL,26,@wD@^OUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
