PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FThe Home Secretary urged the public
OL,8,Fnot to speculate, describing the
OL,9,Fcircumstances as "extremely
OL,10,Fdistressing".
OL,12,FIn a post on X, Shabana Mahmood said:
OL,13,F"I am deeply saddened to hear of the
OL,14,Fdeath of Ann Widdecombe. The
OL,15,Fcircumstances of her death are
OL,16,Fextremely distressing and my thoughts
OL,17,Fare with Ann's family and loved ones.
OL,19,F"Ann's dedication to public service
OL,20,Fwas decades long, and she was a true
OL,21,Fservant of her constituents.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@LO]uD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
