PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,F"I have spoken to the Chief Constable
OL,8,Fof Devon and Cornwall police today.
OL,9,FThe Home Office stands ready to
OL,10,Fprovide whatever support they need
OL,11,Fwith their ongoing investigation.
OL,13,F"I urge everyone to avoid speculation
OL,14,Fand allow the police investigation to
OL,15,Fprogress."
OL,17,FAnn Widdecombe's last media appearance
OL,18,Fwas on Wednesday when she spoke live
OL,19,Fon TalkTV via remote video link.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
