PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FITV News has learnt that Miss
OL,8,FWiddecombe was also due to be a guest,
OL,9,Fvia video call from her home, on
OL,10,FChannel 5's Matt Allwright show at 1pm
OL,11,Fon the same day, but didn't appear.
OL,13,FA researcher on the show had spoken to
OL,14,FMiss Widdecombe on the phone earlier
OL,15,Fin the afternoon to set up the
OL,16,Finterview.
OL,18,FAfter the call, the researcher
OL,19,Fexchanged messages with Miss
OL,20,FWiddecombe, with her last message
OL,21,Freceived at 12:19pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FWhen the researcher then messaged
OL,8,Fagain at 12:48pm requesting that Miss
OL,9,FWiddecombe join the Zoom link in
OL,10,Fpreparation for the remote interview,
OL,11,FMs Widdecombe did not reply.
OL,13,FSubsequent voice calls and messages
OL,14,Fasking if everything was ok remained
OL,15,Funanswered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
