PN,31316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783727306
OL,3,CMan, 26, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after ex-MP Ann Widdecombe
OL,5,Cfound dead
OL,7,FAfter concerns were raised by the
OL,8,Fshow's research team about the
OL,9,Funcharacteristic lack of response by
OL,10,FMiss Widdecombe, who was a regular on
OL,11,Fthe show, they contacted her agent
OL,12,Flater on Wednesday and followed up
OL,13,Fagain on Thursday.
